  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DoubleBinaryOperator
    Performs a double binary operation on two double values.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMatrix
    Abstract implementation of IMatrix.
    AbstractVector
    Abstract implementation of IVector.
    LinAlgDefaults
    Defines creators for default implementations of IVector and IMatrix.
    Matrix
    Simple and concrete implementation of IMatrix using primitive array for storing elements.
    MatrixSubMatrixView
    MatrixSubMatrixView is a live view of a matrix where sum rows and columns are excluded.
    MatrixTransposeView
    MatrixTransposeView is a live view of a transposed matrix.
    MatrixVectorView
    MatrixVectorView creates a new one dimensional matrix live view from a vector.
    Vector
    Simple and concrete implementation of IVector using primitive array for storing elements.
    VectorMatrixView
    VectorMatrixView is a vector live view on one dimensional matrix.
